metadata.name: Toy Boogers Special Edition #1 – OG Booger for Life
metadata.description:
The Toy Boogers Special Edition series is an ongoing Ethereum based NFT airdrop collection for Toy Boogers holders. They are a special way to commemorate big events in the Toy Boogers history. Each Special Edition will be a single work of art with multiple editions. They will be named and numbered by the order in which we create and release them and can be viewed, collected, bought, and sold just like any other Ethereum NFT.

This very first Toy Boogers Special Edition “OG Booger for Life” commemorates and celebrates the earliest supporters and people who minted Toy Boogers during the presale period. The artwork is by Doug, the creator and founder of Toy Boogers. It features the famous and much-loved Stash Hamster which a bunch of Toys. Amongst the Toys is the famous Focusing Crystal and Booger from the Toy Boogers legendary backstory.
